=== ENDING_TOGETHER {
    :: "They open their envelopes at the table. Together."
    :: ""
    :: "Nora cries first. Then Felix."
    :: "Dara holds hers to her chest and looks out at the roses."
    :: ""
    :Nora: "She knew. About all of it."
    :Felix: "She forgave us anyway."
    :Dara: "That's what she did. That's what she always did."
    :: ""
    :: "You close your briefcase."
    :: "The will is clear. The house stays in the family."
    :: "Felix will repay the loan. Nora will stop carrying it alone."
    :: "Dara's studio in the garden shed will keep its light on."
    :: ""
    :: "As you leave, you hear them talking."
    :: "Really talking. For the first time in twelve years."
    :: ""
    :: "{MOTHER}'s roses nod in the rain."
    fin
}

=== ENDING_FRACTURED {
